{"tid":38491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【病人未死喎】殯儀館「搶客」 急診症大打出手","createTime":"2016-12-14T03:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T06:42:50.000Z","uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f5010faa84bd12f238bec73d6468eddb524becd","tid":38491,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161214&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56045017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161214%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56045017&d=g1lacP68hShYVP6FbE%2FDJJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=910366ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161214%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56045017&h=ab3b1398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161214&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56045017</a><br />\n食艱難，想不到殯儀館這般難做，醫院病人還未死，已成搶奪對象。遼寧大連一間醫院早前就發生這樣一場鬧劇，兩間殯儀公司職員因搶客發生爭執，雙方繼而互毆混戰。最離譜的是，他們爭奪的客人還是活着的，正在醫院接受搶救。<br />\n事發於本本月3日上午7時許，救護車將一名病危的患者送到當地醫院，該兩批分別不同殯儀館的人聞訊到場，爭奪該名「未來客人」。他們各不相讓，更在急症室大打出手。警方事後到場將他們帶返派出所調查。警方將參與打鬥的7人，處以行政拘留15日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/767yRb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F767yRb3.jpg&h=1dd1706a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3K4F715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3K4F715.jpg&h=8fd735a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143dcd2471143d2dd73bdda7b27e7c704d4a60a7","tid":38491,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"最終條友有冇死？"},{"pid":"ab9dab81290870f6a89cb6af0a1128188c5e8ced","tid":38491,"uid":32544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"天下事，無奇不有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s